Nguyễn Quốc Thái is a Fresher Mobile Developer with 0.75 years of commercial experience. Their core expertise lies in UI Design, State Management, and Backend Development using Flutter, NestJS, and React-Native, with a strong foundation in programming languages such as Dart, JavaScript, TypeScript, and Java. They have completed a Flutter development course, gaining expertise in Dart, UI design, and advanced Flutter topics, and have expanded their skills to include NestJS, React, JavaScript, TypeScript, and Java for Spring backend development. Notably, they have led a team to develop a movie ticket booking app with Flutter frontend and NestJS backend, utilizing Provider for state management, and have developed personal projects such as a music streaming app and a supercar showroom app, demonstrating their ability to work on diverse projects.

Technically, they are proficient in languages such as Dart, JavaScript, TypeScript, and Java, and have hands-on experience with frameworks and libraries like Flutter, NestJS, React-Native, React-Dom, GetX, Provider, Riverpod, and Spring. They have experience with databases such as SQLite and have worked with devops and cloud platforms like Render and Vietnix. Additionally, they have used tools like Git and Gemini API, and have knowledge of techniques and concepts such as Team Leadership, Task Delegation, Workflow Coordination, and API Integration. Their experience with state management using GetX, Provider, and Riverpod, and their ability to integrate APIs like Gemini API, demonstrate their capability to handle complex technical tasks. With a strong educational background in Computer Science from Ton Duc Thang University and a certification in Toeic 715, Nguyễn Quốc Thái possesses a solid foundation to excel in mobile development and related technologies.